193
00:22:21,145 --> 00:22:26,589
Those people receiving the health care and people dispensing it would not be prosecuted in Medford.

194
00:22:26,609 --> 00:22:30,951
To whatever extent we can protect those rights, we wanted to make sure that we could.

195
00:22:31,751 --> 00:22:36,854
