00:39:46,217 --> 00:39:49,379
Well, I am the sponsor and I've led the effort on this ordinance.

385
00:39:51,139 --> 00:39:55,161
It is been crafted over the last 10 months or so.

386
00:39:55,221 --> 00:39:56,822
I've met with the city treasurer.

387
00:39:56,922 --> 00:40:16,673
