388
00:40:17,994 --> 00:40:19,575
Industries of destruction and violence.

389
00:40:19,716 --> 00:40:25,002
I don't think that's something anyone wants here in our city When we've looked at it, you know

390
00:40:25,673 --> 00:40:29,636
We have gotten legal review from KP Law.

391
00:40:29,696 --> 00:40:32,638
We've gotten legal opinions from a number of sources.

392
00:40:32,678 --> 00:40:38,321
We've had a lot of meetings that have incorporated the legal comments from city legal advisors.

393
00:40:38,842 --> 00:40:43,965
And it's pretty clear that this is an eminently enforceable and clear policy.

394
00:40:44,666 --> 00:40:48,208
There are not many city funds that are actually right now invested in

395
00:40:50,067 --> 00:40:59,476
oil companies, weapons manufacturers, people who are making profits from private prisons, companies that are committing human rights violations across the world.

