00:40:59,916 --> 00:41:06,742
We've actually, in the ordinance, included a condition, a set of conditions from Morgan Stanley.

397
00:41:07,663 --> 00:41:12,107
So if we think this is some radical thing, Morgan Stanley's conditions are the ones that we're using.

398
00:41:12,147 --> 00:41:13,469
That's a Wall Street investment firm.

399
00:41:13,949 --> 00:41:21,514
Because even on Wall Street, they know that our money should not be put into these companies that are committing violence.

400
00:41:21,834 --> 00:41:24,196
And that it's actually not a good return for residents.

401
00:41:24,856 --> 00:41:31,961
The ordinance includes a fiduciary responsibility following all of the relevant state laws.

402
00:41:32,861 --> 00:41:36,144
And in my conversations with the city treasurer, this is easy to enforce.

403
00:41:37,364 --> 00:41:43,948
I don't appreciate the veto and I think we'll work through it collaboratively as I've worked through collaboratively with the mayor on many issues.

